sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API as FastAPI Gateway
    participant Kafka as Kafka Cluster
    participant Validator as Schema Validator
    participant Transformer as Data Transformer
    participant Enricher as Enrichment Pipeline
    participant RuleEngine as Rule Engine
    participant AnomalyDet as Anomaly Detector
    participant MLScorer as ML Risk Scorer
    participant Ensemble as Ensemble Scorer
    participant AlertMgr as Alert Manager
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant Redis as Redis Cache
    participant Notify as Notification Service

    Client->>API: POST /api/v1/transactions
    API->>API: Validate request (Pydantic)
    API->>API: Authenticate (API Key / JWT)
    API->>API: Rate limit check
    API-->>Client: 202 Accepted

    API->>Kafka: Publish to txn.raw.events
    Kafka->>Validator: Consume batch (100 events)
    Validator->>Validator: Schema + business rule checks
    
    alt Invalid Record
        Validator->>Kafka: Route to fraud.dlq
        Validator->>PG: Insert quarantine record
    end

    Validator->>Kafka: Publish to txn.validated
    Kafka->>Transformer: Consume validated events
    Transformer->>Transformer: Clean + Normalize
    Transformer->>Transformer: Engineer 25+ features
    
    Transformer->>Enricher: Pass enrichment request
    Enricher->>Redis: Lookup customer profile
    Redis-->>Enricher: Profile (cache hit)
    Enricher->>Enricher: Geo + Device + Merchant + Velocity
    Enricher->>Kafka: Publish to txn.enriched

    par Parallel Scoring
        Kafka->>RuleEngine: Evaluate 15+ rules
        Kafka->>AnomalyDet: Isolation Forest score
        Kafka->>MLScorer: XGBoost/LightGBM score
    end

    RuleEngine-->>Ensemble: rule_score (0-1)
    AnomalyDet-->>Ensemble: anomaly_score (0-1)
    MLScorer-->>Ensemble: ml_score (0-1)

    Ensemble->>Ensemble: Weighted combination<br/>(0.3R + 0.3A + 0.4ML)
    Ensemble->>Ensemble: Classify risk level
    Ensemble->>PG: Store risk_scores record
    Ensemble->>Kafka: Publish to txn.scored

    alt Risk Score >= HIGH threshold
        Ensemble->>AlertMgr: Generate fraud alert
        AlertMgr->>AlertMgr: Deduplication check
        AlertMgr->>PG: Store fraud_alerts record
        AlertMgr->>Kafka: Publish to fraud.alerts
        AlertMgr->>Notify: Dispatch notification
        Notify->>Notify: Route by severity<br/>(Email/SMS/Webhook)
    end

    Ensemble->>Redis: Update customer profile
    Ensemble->>PG: Update transaction status
